## <span style=color:#28A569>#1</span> Use colour purposefully

A few things to bear in mind

::: {.incremental}
- Accessibility
- Race/Ethnicity - avoid stereotypes and be mindful of unintended messages
- Colour intensity - "more is more"
:::


