## <span style=color:#28A569>#1</span> - Use colour purposefully

:::: {.columns}

::: {.column width=50%}

::: {.fragment}

![](https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/glass-of-orange-juice-with-oranges-1589917191.jpg)
